001C87  1               ; bullet_spr_data — 8x8 4bpp, 32 bytes
001C87  1               ;
001C87  1               ;   Color 0 = transparent, Color 1 = white
001C87  1               ;   Design: 2-pixel-wide vertical bar, centered in 8px columns 3-4
001C87  1               ;
001C87  1               ;   Each byte encodes 2 pixels: high nibble = left, low nibble = right
001C87  1               ;   Columns:  0 1 | 2 3 | 4 5 | 6 7
001C87  1               ;   Pattern:  . . | . 1 | 1 . | . .   → $00 $01 $10 $00
001C87  1               ;   All 8 rows identical.
